flowchart TD
    classDef actor fill:#e0f2fe,stroke:#0369a1,stroke-width:2px;
    classDef system fill:#f8fafc,stroke:#64748b,stroke-width:2px;
    classDef database fill:#fef3c7,stroke:#d97706,stroke-width:2px;
    classDef external fill:#f0fdf4,stroke:#166534,stroke-width:2px;

    Taxpayer((Taxpayer)):::actor
    PolicyTeam((ATO Policy Team)):::actor

    subgraph Portal [ATO Portal - Public Interface]
        Triage[Pre-Chat Triage Form]:::system
        Dial[Creativity Dial]:::system
        Chat[Chatbot Interface]:::system
    end

    subgraph Backend [ATO Advisory AI Service]
        RAG[RAG Engine & LLM]:::system
        PolicyDB[(Public Tax Policy Database)]:::database
    end

    subgraph Verification [Official ATO Resources]
        ATOWeb[Official ATO Website & Legal Database]:::external
    end

    PolicyTeam -->|Maintains & updates| PolicyDB
    
    Taxpayer -->|1. Submits occupation & expense category| Triage
    Triage -->|2. Unlocks chat & passes context| Chat
    
    Taxpayer -->|3. Sets strictness level| Dial
    Dial -->|4. Configures temperature & constraints| RAG
    
    Taxpayer -->|5. Asks deduction question| Chat
    Chat -->|6. Forwards query & triage context| RAG
    
    PolicyDB -->|7. Retrieves relevant tax rulings| RAG
    RAG -->|8. Generates advisory response with citations| Chat
    
    Chat -->|9. Displays guidance, warnings & links| Taxpayer
    Taxpayer -->|10. Clicks citation link to verify| ATOWeb
    ATOWeb -->|11. Provides authoritative policy confirmation| Taxpayer